Former Colombian Finance Minister
Oscar Ivan Zuluaga will run for president in the 2014 election,
El Tiempo said, citing an  interview  with Zuluaga.  Zuluaga told the Bogota-based newspaper that followers of
former President  Alvaro Uribe  will choose someone to run against
President Juan Manuel Santos and that he aims to be that
candidate.  Zuluaga served as Uribeâ€™s finance minister from 2007 to
